storyInfo: The multiple fighting fronts are lit like wildfire, and just as battle seems inevitable, the Saintess Enya elects to descend, quelling the conflict.

attributes.content: Do you come from the Court of Sargon?
attributes.name: Degenbrecher

attributes.content: That was my previous employment.
attributes.name: Sharp

attributes.content: Never thought you'd be able to identify Sargon swordsmanship.
attributes.name: Sharp

attributes.content: I have little interest in Arts. But when it comes to weaponry, I couldn't forget anything, even if I wanted to.
attributes.name: Degenbrecher

attributes.content: No wonder they called The Black Knight a natural-born warrior.
attributes.name: Sharp

attributes.content: Natural-born?
attributes.name: Degenbrecher

attributes.content: Hmph.
attributes.name: Degenbrecher

attributes.content: Do you know how long it took to go from 'a Leithanian who can't use Arts' to 'a natural-born warrior?'
attributes.name: Degenbrecher

attributes.text: The shield in Sharp's hand reveals a crack.
Though there are several wounds on Degenbrecher's body, she seems not to notice them.

attributes.content: Do you have no sense of pain?
attributes.name: Sharp

attributes.content: If growing up, the only waking sensation you knew was pain, then you too would be used to it.
attributes.name: Degenbrecher

attributes.content: How about you? How many times have you danced with death?
attributes.name: Degenbrecher

attributes.content: Everyone I knew who even thought of counting didn't survive long in battle.
attributes.name: Sharp

attributes.content: I heard that The Black Knight, despite being a three-time champion, was exiled from Kazimierz and hunted for refusing to work with the General Chamber of Commerce, eventually disappearing beyond Kazimierz's borders.
attributes.name: Sharp

attributes.content: So?
attributes.name: Degenbrecher

attributes.content: Once a symbol of refusal to bow to authority, now a conspirator's bodyguard taking part in the usurpation of a country.
attributes.name: Sharp

attributes.content: I don't pass any moral judgments. I just can't help but to feel a bit let down.
attributes.name: Sharp

attributes.content: I thought a Rhodes Islander of all people would understand Enciodes's ideas.
attributes.name: Degenbrecher

attributes.content: Understanding is one thing. Acceptance is another.
attributes.name: Sharp

attributes.content: Actually, I think the Doctor understands Enciodes well.
attributes.name: Sharp

attributes.content: I'm not going to defend Enciodes or myself. It's too much of a hassle, and also unnecessary.
attributes.name: Degenbrecher

attributes.content: See for yourself what he wants with your own eyes â€“ if you survive, that is.
attributes.name: Degenbrecher

attributes.content: After a great many struggles, Ensia finally reaches the edge of the cliff. She can scale it easily, but the sound of a nearby conversation makes her freeze.
Everything's gone to shit down there, and everything's gone to shit up here too.
attributes.name: Silverash Clan Warrior A

attributes.content: Yeah. I can't believe the Great Elder went down like that, and now Arctosz is rampaging his way up here.
attributes.name: Silverash Clan Warrior B

attributes.content: I was under the assumption that the worst was over, but now I have no idea what's going to happen next.
attributes.name: Silverash Clan Warrior A

attributes.content: I didn't really think there'd be peace anyway, but now that things have gone south, I feel a little guilty.
attributes.name: Silverash Clan Warrior B

attributes.content: Guilty? Why?
attributes.name: Silverash Clan Warrior A

attributes.content: Since we entered the Vine-Bear Court, the Ladyâ€“â€“ Err, the Saintess, has clearly taken the reins.
attributes.name: Silverash Clan Warrior B

attributes.content: Since the Great Elder collapsed, the entire Vine-Bear Court has fallen in line with the Saintess.
attributes.name: Silverash Clan Warrior B

attributes.content: And below the mountain, Sir Enciodes has taken complete control.
attributes.name: Silverash Clan Warrior B

attributes.content: When you put it that way, it all makes sense, huh. The Saintess controls the mountain, and Sir Enciodes controls everything below.
attributes.name: Silverash Clan Warrior A

attributes.content: Borrowing your words, I have no idea what's going to happen next.
attributes.name: Silverash Clan Warrior B

attributes.content: We're just underlings anyway. There's no point thinking too hard about it.
attributes.name: Silverash Clan Warrior A

attributes.content: Yeah, you're right. Why even bother?
attributes.name: Silverash Clan Warrior B

attributes.content: Let's make two more rounds. Maybe we'll get called down the mountain by then.
attributes.name: Silverash Clan Warrior B

attributes.content: Sis...
attributes.name: Ensia

attributes.content: Hey! What's that?!
attributes.name: Silverash Clan Warrior C

attributes.content: The granary is on fire!
attributes.name: Silverash Clan Warrior D

attributes.content: What?! Someone go put it out, hurry!
attributes.name: Silverash Clan Warrior C

attributes.content: Heh, piece of cake.
attributes.name: Sciurus

attributes.content: Madame, you certainly have a unique way of doing things, though that's to be expected...
attributes.name: Browntail Clan Warrior

attributes.content: The hell are you trying to say?!
attributes.name: Sciurus

attributes.content: N-Nothing, it was a compliment.
attributes.name: Browntail Clan Warrior

attributes.content: Hmph. I'll pay for them to rebuild the granary after we're all done here, but for now, we're on urgent business!
attributes.name: Sciurus

attributes.content: Stop dragging your feet! The fire's got their attention, so go rescue Yucatan! The place is right ahead!
attributes.name: Sciurus

attributes.content: Yes, Madame!
attributes.name: Browntail Clan Warrior

attributes.content: ...Kjarr.
attributes.name: Enya

attributes.content: I'm here, Saintess.
attributes.name: Kjarr

attributes.content: During the ceremony, I recall that when I happened to spot you in the crowd, there was a hooded figure next to you.
attributes.name: Enya

attributes.content: That's right.
attributes.name: Kjarr

attributes.content: I've heard that this person is a guest from Rhodes Island invited by Enciodes. A guest known as the Doctor.
attributes.name: Enya

attributes.content: But now, that individual stands with Arctosz, fighting against Enciodes.
attributes.name: Enya

attributes.content: ...Nothing escapes you, Saintess.
attributes.name: Kjarr

attributes.content: How did you come to know this person?
attributes.name: Enya

attributes.content: By chance, when I was heading down the mountain to deliver your letter.
attributes.name: Kjarr

attributes.content: ...I'll take your word for it then.
attributes.name: Enya

attributes.content: Why did this question suddenly grip your thoughts?
attributes.name: Kjarr

attributes.content: I would like to meet this person.
attributes.name: Enya

attributes.content: Huh?
attributes.name: Kjarr

attributes.content: Though I don't know exactly why, the Doctor stands in direct opposition to Enciodes.
attributes.name: Enya

attributes.content: I want to know exactly why.
attributes.name: Enya

attributes.content: I no longer doubt what I must do, but I am afraid that I made up my mind too late.
attributes.name: Enya

attributes.content: There are some things I must fight for.
attributes.name: Enya

attributes.content: About that... You needn't worry yourself.
attributes.name: Kjarr

attributes.content: Why not?
attributes.name: Enya

attributes.content: Because the Doctor's emissary is right behind you.
attributes.name: Kjarr

attributes.content: Huh?!
attributes.name: Enya

attributes.content: Sis!
attributes.name: Ensia

attributes.content: Ensia... I suppose I've finally started hallucinating.
attributes.name: Enya

attributes.content: Snap out of it, sis! You're not hallucinating! It's me, your sister, Ensia!
attributes.name: Ensia

attributes.content: What?! Ensia, is that really you?
attributes.name: Enya

attributes.content: It is! Here, come touch me if you don't believe it.
attributes.name: Ensia

attributes.content: Enya wants to reach out with her shaking hands to feel Ensia.
She fears that the sister who suddenly appeared before her is an illusion.
But before she has a chance to do so, Ensia has already plunged into her arms.
She knows right away, without a shadow of a doubt, that the woman embracing her is her dearest little sister.
It's you, Ensia... It really is you...
attributes.name: Enya

attributes.content: I've missed you so much.
attributes.name: Ensia

attributes.content: I've missed you too.
attributes.name: Enya

attributes.content: Have you been well?
attributes.name: Enya

attributes.content: What of your illness?
attributes.name: Enya

attributes.content: What kind of place is this Rhodes Island?
attributes.name: Enya

attributes.content: You're so silly. You already asked all these things in your letters.
attributes.name: Ensia

attributes.content: I have to tell you...
attributes.name: Ensia

attributes.content: Sharp takes a few steps back with a shallow breath.
He has fought many opponents throughout his career, and has also learned from â€“ or at least watched â€“Â many formidable fighters at Rhodes Island.
But he has to admit â€“ he has never faced anyone like Degenbrecher before. Or rather, an opponent as pure and simple as Degenbrecher.
She has speed and strength, qualities that every warrior should possess.
Degenbrecher has nothing more, but clearly needs nothing more.
Why would anyone need anything more than incredible speed and strength?
Fortunately... Sharp became an elite operator because he also possesses these two things.
You have a lot of trust in Enciodes.
attributes.name: Sharp

attributes.content: What makes you say that?
attributes.name: Degenbrecher

attributes.content: Few people have the capacity to do this for money.
attributes.name: Sharp

attributes.content: And besides, you are not a person who can be won over with money.
attributes.name: Sharp

attributes.content: What about you? You said this is just business, but what you've done goes well beyond duty.
attributes.name: Degenbrecher

attributes.content: I assure you, the work I do is the work I like.
attributes.name: Sharp

attributes.content: ...I didn't like Kazimierz. Too chaotic, and the people are too loud.
attributes.name: Degenbrecher

attributes.content: I thought I wouldn't like Kjerag either.
attributes.name: Degenbrecher

attributes.content: But Kjerag isn't too bad.
attributes.name: Degenbrecher

attributes.content: That's a fair reason. Having a nice place to retire is important.
attributes.name: Sharp

attributes.content: As if reaching a tacit agreement, the two sides take a few steps back.
They both realize that their previous moves achieved nothing toward the goal of eliminating the opponent.
They would have to tap into more of their power.
Degenbrecher casts her sword aside, and pulls the swordbreakers from her waist.
Sharp likewise discards his shield and holds his knife with both hands.
An evergreen tree branch buckles under the weight of the snow with a crackling sound.
In the same instant, Sharp and Degenbrecher both vanish from where they were just a second ago.
Honestly, what am I going to do with you?
attributes.name: Enya

attributes.content: You actually managed to sneak past everyone and climb all the way up from the foot of the mountain.
attributes.name: Enya

attributes.content: Heheh, it was the only way for me to see you.
attributes.name: Ensia

attributes.content: You were just saying a certain 'the Doctor' sent you up here?
attributes.name: Enya

attributes.content: To what end?
attributes.name: Enya

attributes.content: The Doctor told me I should stay by your side, protect you when you need it, or help you escape.
attributes.name: Ensia

attributes.content: When I need it?
attributes.name: Enya

attributes.content: Yeah, like if our brother tries to do something bad to you.
attributes.name: Ensia

attributes.content: Okay, this is what I think.
attributes.name: Ensia

attributes.content: He has his ideas, and I can't stop him.
attributes.name: Ensia

attributes.content: But if those ideas end up putting you in danger...
attributes.name: Ensia

attributes.content: I'll put my life on the line to stop him.
attributes.name: Ensia

attributes.content: Enya suddenly understands why the Doctor sent her sister to her side.
For protection. For a way out. These are the two reasons told to Ensia.
But the Doctor also knows about her ideals, as well as the fact that being able to see her sister would be inherently meaningful.
Have Ensia protect her?
Have Ensia help her escape?
No, quite the opposite.
She is the one who should protect Ensia.
She is the one who should help Ensia escape.
She is the one â€“â€“ who should be fighting.
Ensia, I see you're still wearing the bracelet I made for you.
attributes.name: Enya

attributes.content: Of course. And I'll keep wearing it.
attributes.name: Ensia

attributes.content: I'll find the time to make a new one for you.
attributes.name: Enya

attributes.content: Really?!
attributes.name: Ensia

attributes.content: Mmhmm.
attributes.name: Enya

attributes.content: So, Ensia...
attributes.name: Enya

attributes.content: Yeah?
attributes.name: Ensia

attributes.content: Do you want to do a little favor for me?
attributes.name: Enya

attributes.content: A favor?
attributes.name: Ensia

attributes.content: Come with me.
attributes.name: Enya

attributes.content: (It's awfully quiet outside, but there should still be two guards.)
attributes.name: Yucatan

attributes.content: (The window... If I don't want them to see me from this angle, I have to lead the guards away first.)
attributes.name: Yucatan

attributes.content: (The patrol route... They pass through this area five times a day, and should be coming around soon.)
attributes.name: Yucatan

attributes.content: (No, I can't force open the lock... But if I can pick it...)
attributes.name: Yucatan

attributes.content: (...Then there might still be a chance.)
attributes.name: Yucatan

attributes.content: Sir Enciodes... This time I swear...
attributes.name: Young Guard

attributes.content: (â€“â€“They're coming!)
attributes.name: Yucatan

attributes.content: The conflict... three clans seems inevitable, but...
attributes.name: Young Guard

attributes.content: ...Browntail clan's... burning... Sciurus...
attributes.name: Older Guard

attributes.content: (Sciurus...?!)
attributes.name: Yucatan

attributes.content: (Why did they mention Rus? Did something happen to her?!)
attributes.name: Yucatan

attributes.content: (Dammit, I'm still too far away... I can't hear clearly.)
attributes.name: Yucatan

attributes.content: (No, she can handle herself. I have to find a way out of here first, then find Sciurus and the Matriarch...)
attributes.name: Yucatan

attributes.content: Halt, who are you people?!
attributes.name: Silverash Clan Warrior

attributes.content: Stop them right nowâ€“â€“ Guh...
attributes.name: Silverash Clan Warrior

attributes.content: (There's a commotion coming from the entrance... What happened?)
attributes.name: Yucatan

attributes.content: Yucatan, are you alright?!
attributes.name: Sciurus

attributes.content: Rus?! What are you doing here?
attributes.name: Yucatan

attributes.content: Huh? Are you dumb? I'm here for you, obviously!
attributes.name: Sciurus

attributes.content: Everyone else is so worthless, I had to rescue you myself!
attributes.name: Sciurus

attributes.content: But, it's too dangerous!
attributes.name: Yucatan

attributes.content: Rus, how many did you bring with you? Y-You didn't have to come yourself, you know. I wouldn't want anything to happen to you!
attributes.name: Yucatan

attributes.content: Yucatan.
attributes.name: Sciurus

attributes.content: Say one more word and I'm going to beat the crap out of you.
attributes.name: Sciurus

attributes.content: Umm...
attributes.name: Yucatan

attributes.content: Shut up! Think about what you'd do for me. I'll do just the same for you!
attributes.name: Sciurus

attributes.content: And you'd better not forget it!
attributes.name: Sciurus

attributes.content: Also, you're not allowed to abandon me ever again.
attributes.name: Sciurus

attributes.content: Rus...
attributes.name: Yucatan

attributes.content: You know I'd never do that.
attributes.name: Yucatan

attributes.content: Hmph! Of course I know!
attributes.name: Sciurus

attributes.content: Alright, the fact that you're okay is a huge load off my shoulders... Now, I have something else to take care of. I promised Ratatos I'd finish another job after I save you.
attributes.name: Sciurus

attributes.content: A job?
attributes.name: Yucatan

attributes.content: Madame Sciurus, Weiss of the Silverash clan is moving to intercept us!
attributes.name: Browntail Clan Warrior

attributes.content: Right on schedule. I'll tell you the details later, but our job is to cause some trouble for those Silverash bastards.
attributes.name: Sciurus

attributes.content: And... there's someone else I want to talk to. But that comes later!
attributes.name: Sciurus

attributes.content: Things aren't looking too good, and Weiss won't go down easy... But we're in this together. Right, Yucatan?
attributes.name: Sciurus

attributes.content: Of course. I'll be there for you as long as you need me.
attributes.name: Yucatan

attributes.content: Close in on them!
attributes.name: Matterhorn

attributes.content: Don't let Arctosz up the mountain path!
attributes.name: Matterhorn

attributes.content: Sir, we're about to be completely encircled!
attributes.name: Paleroche Clan Warrior

attributes.content: Hmph... I suppose this is as far as we could get just charging through.
attributes.name: Arctosz

attributes.content: Please lay down your arms, Arctosz.
attributes.name: Matterhorn

attributes.content: Child of Yek, I don't know what Enciodes offered you to make you so infatuated with him.
attributes.name: Arctosz

attributes.content: The Yek family is prominent in Paleroche lands.
attributes.name: Arctosz

attributes.content: Yet you still chose to help Enciodes usurp Kjerag!
attributes.name: Arctosz

attributes.content: Lay down my arms?
attributes.name: Arctosz

attributes.content: Never.
attributes.name: Arctosz

attributes.content: Arrest Arctosz... But try to take him alive.
attributes.name: Matterhorn

attributes.content: Come at me, Silverash scum! Who's brave enough to face me?!
attributes.name: Arctosz

attributes.content: ...Aurora?!
attributes.name: Matterhorn

attributes.content: Does that meanâ€“â€“
attributes.name: Matterhorn

attributes.options: Looks like I caught up to you.;Hey.;(Tug on the brim of your hood)

attributes.content: Doctorâ€“â€“?!
attributes.name: Matterhorn

attributes.content: Don't tell me, Degenbrecher...
attributes.name: Matterhorn

attributes.content: Ah, Doctor, it's about damned time!
attributes.name: Arctosz

attributes.options: The snow delayed things a bit.;Avoiding Silverash eyes and ears took time.

attributes.content: Haha, Kjerag's snow is a challenge for outsiders like you.
attributes.name: Arctosz

attributes.content: No worries. All that matters is that you're here!
attributes.name: Arctosz

attributes.content: Heh, now that reinforcements are here, nothing can stop us!
attributes.name: Arctosz

attributes.content: Isn't it too early to celebrate, Arctosz?
attributes.name: Enciodes

attributes.content: Enciodes!
attributes.name: Arctosz

attributes.content: Long time no see, Doctor.
attributes.name: Enciodes

attributes.options: 'Long time no see' indeed.;Has it really been that long?;So, you're finally willing to meet me.

attributes.content: Though there's a lot I want to talk to you about, now is not the time, unfortunately.
attributes.name: Enciodes

attributes.content: Just you wait, Enciodes. I'll break through your encirclement, rescue the Saintess, and prove to all of Kjerag that you're the real traitor!
attributes.name: Arctosz

attributes.content: Iâ€™m looking forward to it.
attributes.name: Enciodes

attributes.content: Warriors, what has been the house of Paleroche's duty since the beginning of time?
attributes.name: Arctosz

attributes.content: 'Defend Kjerag from foreign enemies, and protect the peace of the land!'
Now, Enciodes seeks to work against the Saintess and use her as his tool.
attributes.name: Arctosz

attributes.content: Can we, the hosue of Paleroche, accept that?
attributes.name: Arctosz

attributes.content: 'No! No! Absolutely not!!!'
Reinforcements have arrived. Follow me up Mount Karlan, topple Enciodes, and rescue the Saintess!
attributes.name: Arctosz

attributes.content: 'Topple Enciodes, rescue the Saintess!'
'Topple Enciodes, rescue the Saintess!!'
'Topple Enciodes, rescue the Saintess!!!'
Saintess, what are you doing?!
attributes.name: Silverash Clan Warrior

attributes.content: I'm heading down the mountain.
attributes.name: Enya

attributes.content: Sir Enciodes saidâ€“â€“
attributes.name: Silverash Clan Warrior

attributes.content: Since when do I need Enciodes's consent to do things?
attributes.name: Enya

attributes.content: 'Ding ding', 'ding ding', 'ding dingâ€“â€“'
An otherworldly bell sounds throughout the court.
The next moment, everyone present except Ensia falls to the ground.
Wow... incredible...
attributes.name: Ensia

attributes.content: Kjarr, Kjarr.
attributes.name: Enya

attributes.content: Saintess, how did you know I was here?
attributes.name: Kjarr

attributes.content: I can guess where a clever girl hides.
attributes.name: Enya

attributes.content: I need to make a trip down the mountain, so please look after things here.
attributes.name: Enya

attributes.content: Oh, are you leaving the hard work to me?
attributes.name: Kjarr

attributes.content: There are even more troublesome things waiting for me.
attributes.name: Enya

attributes.content: If that's the case, I suppose I can't object.
attributes.name: Kjarr

attributes.content: In fact, during each Saintess selection, I'd dress up as a maid and secretly observe the girls being tested.
attributes.name: Kjarr

attributes.content: You were the sixth one that year.
attributes.name: Kjarr

attributes.content: I didn't have very high expectations for you, at first, since the Saintesses have been more and more boring as of late.
attributes.name: Kjarr

attributes.content: They may have been strong of body, but none of them were sufficiently strong of will and all ended up puppets of the Elders.
attributes.name: Kjarr

attributes.content: I sometimes wonder if this is because Kjerag is too closed-off. They, and the people of this country too, stagnated.
attributes.name: Kjarr

attributes.content: But you're different.
attributes.name: Kjarr

attributes.content: You're very interesting, Enya.
attributes.name: Kjarr

attributes.content: You didn't come here because you wanted to be the Saintess, but because of your anger and disappointment.
attributes.name: Kjarr

attributes.content: You faced the unforgiving elements on the trail up the mountain, you refused to give up even when your body had reached its limits, the thing on your mind...
attributes.name: Kjarr

attributes.content: Was not becoming a Saintess, or becoming an envoy of Kjeragandr. Rather, you were thinking about how best to serve the Kjerag people.
attributes.name: Kjarr

attributes.content: You thought about how disappointed you were in your brother, how disgusted you were with the other two clans, and the rage you felt at becoming the Saintess.
attributes.name: Kjarr

attributes.content: But the real surprise was your attitude towards Kjerag.
attributes.name: Kjarr

attributes.content: Or more accurately, the surprise that your family brought me.
attributes.name: Kjarr

attributes.content: Your brother gave me his answer sheet very early on.
attributes.name: Kjarr

attributes.content: And you have been searching for your own answers this entire time.
attributes.name: Kjarr

attributes.content: Over the years, you've endured the indifference with which the Saintess is treated in the Vine-Bear Court, while actively searching for a way to help the people. These things have become your nourishment.
attributes.name: Kjarr

attributes.content: And now, all that nourishment has transformed into your strength. You have not lost yourself amidst the turmoil, and you have made your choice.
attributes.name: Kjarr

attributes.content: Congratulations, my child, my envoy, my friend, my sister.
attributes.name: Kjarr

attributes.content: Forgive me for not being able to guide you. I rashly branded this land with my mark, and still regret it to this day.
attributes.name: Kjarr

attributes.content: But at least, allow me to add some color to your journey.
attributes.name: Kjarr

attributes.content: Above the silent passageway, Kjarr smiles and gently pats her hands together.
'Clap, clap.'
After which, everything changes.
Just a scratch!
attributes.name: Gulo

attributes.content: Ugh...
attributes.name: Valais

attributes.content: Valais, I'm not sure if Master Arctosz wronged you in some wayâ€“â€“
attributes.name: Gulo

attributes.content: But Enciodes isn't exactly a saint himself!
attributes.name: Gulo

attributes.content: I already told you.
attributes.name: Valais

attributes.content: Kjerag needs change.
attributes.name: Valais

attributes.content: This is also so that excellent warriors like yourself will no longer make sacrifices in vain!
attributes.name: Valais

attributes.content: Don't force my hand, Valais.
attributes.name: Gulo

attributes.content: That's my line, Gulo.
attributes.name: Valais

attributes.content: The two of them take a step back and assume a solid stance.
They know that today, one of them must fall.
What's that?
attributes.name: Gulo

attributes.content: The dark cloud... cleared?
attributes.name: Valais

attributes.content: Gah... What a stubborn one. I underestimated you.
attributes.name: Weiss

attributes.content: But, even if you manage to defeat us here, it won't make any difference.
attributes.name: Weiss

attributes.content: You cannot stop the Master.
attributes.name: Weiss

attributes.content: Like I care.
attributes.name: Yucatan

attributes.content: The Matriarch... Ratatos always had her own ideas about Kjerag.
attributes.name: Yucatan

attributes.content: She also wants people to move forward and hopes that everyone can have a better future.
attributes.name: Yucatan

attributes.content: Except, she doesn't have the power.
attributes.name: Yucatan

attributes.content: And so, she became Ratatos the schemer, as you people call her.
attributes.name: Yucatan

attributes.content: Maybe to you, my sister is just a bump in the road.
attributes.name: Yucatan

attributes.content: But to me, she'll always be my beloved sister!
attributes.name: Yucatan

attributes.content: Yucatan...
attributes.name: Sciurus

attributes.content: We don't hold any personal grudges against you. As long as you're willing to lay down your arms, we guarantee your safety.
attributes.name: Weiss

attributes.content: I'm not going to let Rus and I become bargaining chips for Enciodes to use against the Matriarch.
attributes.name: Yucatan

attributes.content: Weiss of the Silverash clan, step aside, or I will kill you.
attributes.name: Yucatan

attributes.content: The same goes for you, Yucatan of the Browntail clan.
attributes.name: Weiss

attributes.content: You must remain here.
attributes.name: Weiss

attributes.content: You can do it, Yucatan!
attributes.name: Sciurus

attributes.content: Huh...?
attributes.name: Sciurus

attributes.content: Look, Mount Karlan! Are those dark clouds clearing up?!
attributes.name: Sciurus

attributes.content: Sharp turns and watches Degenbrecher slowly return her swordbreakers to her waist.
Around them, trees lie snapped in twain and rocks shattered as if a Catastrophe swept through the land.
He doesn't notice his knife slipping, because he has already lost feeling in his right hand.
He has lost.
Best not overuse your right hand for the next three months.
attributes.name: Degenbrecher

attributes.content: Thanks for the tip. Looks like it's time to take a brief medical leave.
attributes.name: Sharp

attributes.content: You don't seem very upset about it.
attributes.name: Degenbrecher

attributes.content: The outcome of our fight here doesn't change anything.
attributes.name: Sharp

attributes.content: I kept you occupied here until now, so I've done my job. The others will handle the rest.
attributes.name: Sharp

attributes.content: Now that my job's done, it's time to clock out.
attributes.name: Sharp

attributes.content: Is your job that important to you?
attributes.name: Degenbrecher

attributes.content: Maintaining professionalism is very important to me.
attributes.name: Sharp

attributes.content: Finding a good employer isn't easy, so I do happen to care about this job.
attributes.name: Sharp

attributes.content: What about you? You knew from the beginning that I was here to waste your time. You don't look that upset about it.
attributes.name: Sharp

attributes.content: Call it a bit of curiosity. Even if you managed to delay me here, what exactly can you accomplish?
attributes.name: Degenbrecher

attributes.content: Looks like, Enciodes's bodyguards are good for doing more than just his dirty work.
attributes.name: Sharp

attributes.content: People only know that Enciodes bought The Black Knight. They don't know the Black Knight also approves of Enciodes.
attributes.name: Sharp

attributes.content: You and Enciodes are both prideful.
attributes.name: Sharp

attributes.content: ...I'll remember your name, Sharp.
attributes.name: Degenbrecher

attributes.content: You don't have to remember my name, but you would do well to remember the Doctor's.
attributes.name: Sharp

attributes.content: Hm?
attributes.name: Degenbrecher

attributes.content: What's going on at Mount Karlan?
attributes.name: Sharp

attributes.content: Soldiers, in formation.
attributes.name: Arctosz

attributes.content: Yessir!
attributes.name: Paleroche Clan Warriors

attributes.content: All forcesâ€“â€“
attributes.name: Enciodes

attributes.content: What happened?
attributes.name: Arctosz

attributes.content: Time seems to stand still in this moment.
Only the Saintess's footsteps reverberate through the mountains.
The wind and snow already gave way, at some unknown time.
The dark clouds overhead seem to part before her path, slowly spreading to both sides.
The light filtering through the clouds shines upon the Saintess, and for a second, the people see her descending from the sky itself.
But this is no illusion.
A miracle...
It's a miracle.
It's a miracle!!!
In this moment, only one thought remains in the hearts of the warriors.
And that is â€“â€“ to offer their staunchest devotion to the Saintess.
Kjarr.
attributes.name: Servant

attributes.content: Go. I will attend to the Great Elder.
attributes.name: Kjarr

attributes.content: Of course.
attributes.name: Servant

attributes.content: Come to think of it, even though the great hall has been repaired several times, it may not be much younger than Her.
attributes.name: Kjarr

attributes.content: The same goes for the title of Great Elder.
attributes.name: Kjarr

attributes.content: No one would deny that the existence of the Vine-Bear Court has allowed Kjerag to remain united all these years.
attributes.name: Kjarr

attributes.content: But what was correct in the past may no longer be correct.
attributes.name: Kjarr

attributes.content: If you cannot adapt to the changing times, then no matter how strong you are, you are fated to be cast aside.
attributes.name: Kjarr

attributes.content: Kjerag should not suffer that fate. At least, that is what some people hope.
attributes.name: Kjarr

attributes.content: Sweet dreams, Great Elder.
attributes.name: Kjarr

attributes.content: You've done well. You've all done well.
attributes.name: Kjarr

attributes.content: ...How?
attributes.name: Valais

attributes.content: ...What is THAT?
attributes.name: Gulo

attributes.content: Is that... a miracle...?
attributes.name: Gulo

attributes.content: What's going on at Mount Karlan?
attributes.name: Weiss

attributes.content: All forces, pull back.
attributes.name: Weiss

attributes.content: What... just happened?
attributes.name: Sciurus

attributes.content: Can it be... a miracle from Kjeragandr?
attributes.name: Yucatan

attributes.content: What will happen to Kjerag now...?
attributes.name: Ratatos

attributes.content: Hurts my eyes.
attributes.name: Degenbrecher

attributes.content: You've got me wondering now. Is this also a part of your Doctor's plans?
attributes.name: Degenbrecher

attributes.content: I don't know myself.
attributes.name: Sharp

attributes.content: To be honest, if this was a part of the Doctor's plans, or even an anticipated possibility...
attributes.name: Sharp

attributes.content: Even if some operators act like the Doctor is omnipotent, I think this would be a bridge too far.
attributes.name: Sharp

attributes.content: Enya, I'm scared...
attributes.name: Ensia

attributes.content: Don't be, Ensia.
attributes.name: Enya

attributes.content: I will protect you.
attributes.name: Enya

attributes.content: I... will protect Kjerag.
attributes.name: Enya

attributes.content: All the warriors along the mountain trail lay their weapons down.
In the face of a miracle from the Goddess of the Snowy Mountains, the goddess they have worshipped all their lives, their mortal squabbles seem ridiculous.
I, leader of the Paleroche clan, Arctosz Paleroche, offer my most sincere blessings to Her envoy, the Saintess.
attributes.name: Arctosz

attributes.content: After a short silence, he slowly bows to the Saintess and kneels before her.
All the Paleroche warriors follow his lead, repeating his actions.
...Having second thoughts now, Enciodes?
attributes.name: Gnosis

attributes.content: What do you mean?
attributes.name: Enciodes

attributes.content: You ignored my advice and brought that Doctor to Kjerag.
attributes.name: Gnosis

attributes.content: Do you think we lost?
attributes.name: Enciodes

attributes.content: Does this not seem like a loss to you?
attributes.name: Gnosis

attributes.content: It might have, in the past.
attributes.name: Enciodes

attributes.content: But today... maybe not.
attributes.name: Enciodes

attributes.content: Enciodes steps forward.
He strides out from the crowd and also approaches the Saintess, taking a knee and offering his blessings.
All the warriors of the Silverash clan follow suit.
And thus, the Snowcap Incident comes to an unexpected conclusion.
